plicable as per the terms.<\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-9e5c06d elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"9e5c06d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Refund Terms and Conditions<\/h4>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-31cbd5d elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"31cbd5d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<ul>\n<li>Eligibility for Refund: To be eligible for a refund, the candidate must have formally enrolled in the Job Guarantee Plan provided by Netbounce. Netbounce is not obligated to issue any refund if the candidate failsto meet theirresponsibilities as specified in the agreement.<\/li>\n<li>Refund Percentage: If Netbounce fails to secure between 5 to 10 interviews to candidate by its services candidate is eligible for a refund equivalent to 70%. If Netbounce successfully secures between 11 to 15 interviews to candidate through its services candidate is eligible for a refund equivalent to 50%.<\/li>\n<li>Expense: The refund will be subjected to a deduction of less a monthly charge of $375, as stipulated in the agreement. This fee compensates for promotional campaigns, recruiter time, and backend systems utilized. The deduction will be made proportionally based on the duration of services rendered.<\/li>\n<li>Request for Refund: Candidate who meet the refund criteria must formally request a refund by submitting a written request to Netbounce on <a href=\"mailto:foryou@netbounceplacement.com\"><strong>foryou@netbounceplacement.com<\/strong><\/a><\/li>\n<li>Refund Processing Time: Upon a valid refund request, Netbounce will review the request and verify the candidate\u2019s eligibility.Once eligibility is confirmed,the refund will be processed within 30 days.<\/li>\n<li>Cancellation of Enrollment: It&#8217;simportant to note that if a candidate chooses to cancel their enrollment in the Job Guarantee Plan during its term, no refund will be initiated, and the candidate will not be eligible for a refund under these terms and conditions.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>REFUND POLICY Home REFUND POLICY As per the agreement, please note that we do not offer refunds in No Job Gaurantee Plans*, and all sales are considered final. The candidate needs to understand and acknowledge that refunds are only applicable if the candidate chooses to enroll in our Job Guarantee Plan, which is subject to [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"footnotes":""},"class_list":["post-2120","page","type-page","status-publish","hentry"],"aioseo_notices":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.netbounceplacement.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/2120","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.netbounceplacement.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.netbounceplacement.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.netbounceplacement.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.netbounceplacement.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=2120"}],"version-history":[{"count":7,"href":"https:\/\/www.netbounceplacement.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/2120\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":2150,"href":"https:\/\/www.netbounceplacement.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/2120\/revisions\/2150"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.netbounceplacement.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=2120"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}